results.message: Hi
Hey friend, how are you?
I wanted to share something with you
I have some news
I'm not doing too good

I got praised at work today!
I finally finished that big project
I got promoted! I want to celebrate this moment
My friend upset me today
I don't feel understood at home
My friends met up without me and it triggered abandonment feelings
A close friend said something hurtful and I'm unsure how to rebuild trust
I'm noticing misalignment and grieving the drifting of a friendship
I had a lovely day with my mum

I'm making a new friend and feel excited but unsure
I had a disagreement with my dad that brought up old childhood patterns

I'm caring for my elderly parent and feel exhausted and guilty
I'm doing everything right but still feel misunderstood by my family
I love my partner but feel hurt after our argument
I'm in a new relationship and have butterflies mixed with fear

I'm grieving my pet who passed away

My home feels really chaotic
Laundry, dishes, clutter - everything feels like a mountain
I'm moving and feel stressed, excited, and nostalgic
I had a conflict with my neighbor over noise
I don't feel safe in my home environment
I feel so grateful for my home space

An unexpected bill arrived and I feel panicked
I'm worried about making rent this month
I'm considering a big financial decision and feel confused
I received unexpected money and feel grateful
I'm feeling anxious but don't know why
I'm tired of feeling tired all the time
I had a successful therapy session with breakthroughs
I'm struggling with feeling not enough
I noticed I handled something better than I used to
I'm feeling really anxious
I feel completely hopeless
I can't cope anymore
Someone is bullying me at school
I hurt someone and I feel guilty
I lost control and snapped at them
I'm overwhelmed by homework and feel pressure piling up
I'm stressed about exams and afraid of failing
I'm struggling to focus in class
I got a good grade and want to share this win
I had a misunderstanding with my teacher
I'm falling behind in school and feel ashamed to ask for help
I'm starting a new school and feel nervous and hopeful
I saw my friends talking in a group chat without me
Rumors are being spread about me and I feel hurt
My best friend is drifting away and I can't explain why
I have social anxiety and overthink everything at school
I got invited to something but I'm nervous about going
I'm arguing with my parents and feel unheard
My sibling keeps crossing my boundaries
My parents are pushing too hard and I'm burnt out
My parents are divorcing and I'm trying to make sense of it
I feel invisible at home, my emotions are dismissed
I had my first heartbreak and it hurts so much
I'm overthinking every interaction with my crush
They just ghosted me without explanation
I feel pressured to do things I'm not ready for
I feel insecure about my body
I don't feel good enough
I'm trying to understand who I am
I feel different and don't fit in any boxes
Nothing feels exciting, everything feels heavy
Someone left harsh comments online and it really stings
I posted something embarrassing and can't stop thinking about it
I know I scroll too much but can't stop
There's drama in our group chat with screenshots and misunderstandings
I have performance anxiety before my sports event
I didn't get chosen for the team and feel rejected
I made something I'm proud of but shy to share
I keep comparing myself to more talented peers
I feel pressure to achieve for my family's reputation
I'm the first in my family going to university
My family wants me to be a doctor but I want something else
I have to translate and help my parents with everything
I want independence but feel guilty about cultural duty
In my culture we don't talk about emotions openly
I struggle to express complex feelings in English
I feel caught between cultures, not enough for either side
People mock my accent and it hurts
I'm mixed heritage and trying to belong to multiple places
I'm navigating religious rules and guilt around my choices
My parents migrated and sacrificed so much for me
I'm excited about our cultural festival and want to share traditions
I'm proud of my heritage and want to share my culture
I experienced racism today and feel deeply hurt
I keep experiencing microaggressions and feel unsafe
People keep asking where I'm really from
I received online hate because of my ethnicity
I feel disconnected from my spiritual traditions
People judge my spiritual practices
I'm going through a spiritual coming-of-age ceremony
I've had a bad week
I've been struggling for 3 months
I want to hurt myself
I don't want to be here anymore
